        "content": "<p>Hi everyone.<br>\nI am trying to show some object <code>M</code> is a commutative monoid with zero in lean3, but I already know <code>M</code> is a commutative monoid. What is the best way to write it (only provide new information) ? I only know the way to use the underline then generates skeleton for the structure then fill all the holes.</p>",
